{"tid":1841393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔封關，醫護就應該罷工...咁不如全港三罷啦","createTime":"2020-01-25T08:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T11:21:38.000Z","uid":267178,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5155f0ecc2e7e4c0d2aecb02b95b75d46433a2c","tid":1841393,"uid":267178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:57:30.000Z","msg":"雖然醫護罷工好有影響力，但係唔一定要佢哋全部承擔。可以考慮全港三罷。<br />\n<br />\n一來三罷對政府有壓力（三罷包括醫護人員），二來如果繼續唔封關，大家搭車同返工都有好大危險。三罷留喺屋企就最安全，隔離自己，唔洗俾人感染，又唔會傳病毒俾人。<br />\n<br />\n宜家已經唔只係政治問題，而係性命問題。但係我唔知應該邊日開始三罷，例如年初四會唔會太趕。"},{"pid":"8d8a3fb24b8d416bda2e44d931d04e806cab4654","tid":1841393,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"【第廿叄期牆紙x民記】黃色經濟起革命 良心消費衛我城<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1833670/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1833670/page/1</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FbktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=c3ad0f13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FbktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=07df0c6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pyqDTS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyqDTS2.jpg&h=6706d986&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bea04ec6f44415be696a085e7d4d8ed2dc333101","tid":1841393,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:58:47.000Z","msg":"越早越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拖一日就多一個中招"},{"pid":"db81cf0613a498cead4055eadee7b11f61cf9591","tid":1841393,"uid":267178,"like":1,"dislik